abstract: Sergey V. Lavrov is set to visit the White House on Tuesday afternoon, for a conversation that could include extending the last major nuclear treaty between the United States and Russia.
snippet: Sergey V. Lavrov is set to visit the White House on Tuesday afternoon, for a conversation that could include extending the last major nuclear treaty between the United States and Russia.
lead_paragraph: WASHINGTON — The last time President Trump met in the Oval Office with Sergey V. Lavrov, the Russian foreign minister, it did not go so well.

abstract: A Republican congressman says there isn’t one — and that suggests how history will remember it. But historians disagree.
snippet: A Republican congressman says there isn’t one — and that suggests how history will remember it. But historians disagree.
lead_paragraph: WASHINGTON — Representative Doug Collins of Georgia, trying to minimize the impeachment investigation of President Trump on Monday, pointed to the lack of memorable lines uttered by participants compared with impeachments past.

abstract: There are things more important than your tax rate.
snippet: There are things more important than your tax rate.
lead_paragraph: On Saturday Donald Trump gave a speech to the Israeli American Council in which he asserted that many in his audience were “not nice people at all,” but that “you have to vote for me” because Democrats would raise their taxes.

abstract: Some of the findings were already known. But they are sure to fuel a debate over when, and how, to end the American-led war.
snippet: Some of the findings were already known. But they are sure to fuel a debate over when, and how, to end the American-led war.
lead_paragraph: WASHINGTON — The war in Afghanistan has cost American taxpayers more than $1 trillion, but has produced at best a faltering democracy and — most tragically — has resulted in the deaths of nearly 115,000 civilians, military forces, humanitarian aid workers and journalists.
